title: Efficient Labor Regulations
description: In 2024, Morocco achieved a score of 32.17 in the operational efficiency of labor regulations and public services, indicating a high level of efficiency in this area.

title: Minimal Tariff Lines with Specific Rates
description: In 2021, only 0.0008% of Morocco's tariff lines for all products had specific rates, one of the lowest in the world.

title: Low Tariff Specific Rates for Primary Products
description: In 2021, Morocco had just 0.007% of its tariff lines for primary products with specific rates, showcasing minimal use of specific tariffs.
